rupture important, allant jusqu'&#x00E0; 25%, ont &#x00E9;t&#x00E9; constat&#x00E9;s dans certains &#x00E9;tablissements signataires.&nbsp;</p><p>Cet amendement vise &#x00E0; garantir que les agents en charge du contr&#x00F4;le du BQP&nbsp;veillent &#x00E0; la qualit&#x00E9; et &#x00E0; la disponibilit&#x00E9; des produits dans les rayons.&nbsp;</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-11-29", "datePublication": "2024-12-04", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Adopt\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2024-12-04T11:32:50+01:00", "sort": "Adopt\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO419610B0522P0D1N000017?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}